high_descs: Move to the sink to the right
Pick up the knife from the counter
Turn right and move to the microwave
open the microwave, cut the apple inside then close the microwave
Move slightly to the left
Open the microwave and place the knife inside to the left of the apple
Move slightly to the right
Open the microwave and remove a slice of apple then close the microwave
Go to the fridge just to the right of the microwave
Open the fridge, place the apple slice just below the lettuce and close the fridge door, wait a bit then open the door and remove the apple slice, close the fridge door
Turn left and go to the microwave
open the microwave, put the slice in to the left of the apple then close the microwave door
anns.task_desc: Preparing an apple and putting it in the microwave

high_descs: Turn right, go towards the microwave, hang a left and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter in front of the sink.
Turn around and head to the microwave that is on the left.
Use the knife to cut the apple that is inside the microwave, close the microwave.
Move over to the left in front of the microwave.
Put the knife inside the microwave behind the apple, close the microwave.
Move over to the right in front of the microwave.
Take a piece of apple out of the microwave.
Hang a right and head to the fridge.
Put the apple inside the fridge and close the door, remove the cold apple from the fridge.
Turn to the left and head to the microwave.
Put the cold piece of apple inside the microwave.
Walk towards the sink
Grab the knife from the sink
Walk towards the microwave
Slice apple in the microwave
Walk back and turn, come back to the microwave
Put knife in the microwave
Close the microwave door, walk back to the microwave
Grab apple slice from the microwave
Walk with the apple slice to the fridge
Put the apple slice in the fridge, close it and take the apple slice again
Walk with the apple slice towards the microwave
Put the apple slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Slice the apple in the microwave, put a slice in the fridge, and put it in the microwave
